    "result": {"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h1>HOC</h1>\n<hr>\n<p>리액트를 사용하다 보면 중복된 로직을 갖는 컴포넌트가 종종 나온다. 예를 들면 이런 식인데</p>\n<p>A.js 컴포넌트\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/de34d/1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 36.97916666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/a59e9/1.webp 192w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/0ca9f/1.webp 384w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/dc9b9/1.webp 768w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/e2c2f/1.webp 1152w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/f3efb/1.webp 1536w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/54a31/1.webp 2042w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/3b721/1.png 192w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/66595/1.png 384w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/fe486/1.png 768w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/d2d74/1.png 1152w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/e8464/1.png 1536w,\n/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/de34d/1.png 2042w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/b23a292c44b3d8998872a8d71cbf1baf/fe486/1.png\" alt=\"1\" title=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>B.js 컴포넌트\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/de34d/2.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 39.583333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/a59e9/2.webp 192w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/0ca9f/2.webp 384w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/dc9b9/2.webp 768w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/e2c2f/2.webp 1152w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/f3efb/2.webp 1536w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/54a31/2.webp 2042w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/3b721/2.png 192w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/66595/2.png 384w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/fe486/2.png 768w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/d2d74/2.png 1152w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/e8464/2.png 1536w,\n/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/de34d/2.png 2042w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/a067b48f9e12a04f300efdf6a131c4b4/fe486/2.png\" alt=\"2\" title=\"2\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>A 컴포넌트와 B 컴포넌트는 onClick의 핸들러 함수 이외에 다른 차이점이 없다.</p>\n<p>아주 약간의 다른 점 때문에 전체 코드를 다시 작성해야 하는 불편함을 어떤 식으로 해소할 수 있을지 찾아보았다.</p>\n<p>그러던 중 <strong>HOC (higher order component)</strong> 라는 개념에 대해 알게 됐다. HOC란 컴포넌트를 인자로 받아 새로운 컴포넌트로 반환하는 컴포넌트임을 의미한다. HOC를 사용해서 위 중복 로직을 제거하고 컴포넌트를 재사용해 보자.</p>\n<p>먼저 컴포넌트를 인자로 받기 위한 HOC 컴포넌트를 새로 생성한다. HOC 컴포넌트는 기존 컴포넌트와의 차이를 위해 이름에 with을 붙인다고 한다.</p>\n<br/>\n<p>withCounter.js 컴포넌트\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/5dea3/3.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 43.22916666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/a59e9/3.webp 192w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/0ca9f/3.webp 384w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/dc9b9/3.webp 768w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/e2c2f/3.webp 1152w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/f3efb/3.webp 1536w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/18d98/3.webp 2312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/3b721/3.png 192w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/66595/3.png 384w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/fe486/3.png 768w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/d2d74/3.png 1152w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/e8464/3.png 1536w,\n/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/5dea3/3.png 2312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/2f84910b372974322fdd7f45a8e8dcd6/fe486/3.png\" alt=\"3\" title=\"3\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>withCounter 컴포넌트 내부에 WrapperComponent를 반환하는 함수를 선언한다.\n그리고 해당 함수에서 중복 로직을 정의해 주었다. 이제 A와 B 컴포넌트를 보면</p>\n<p>A.js 컴포넌트\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/5dea3/4.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 32.8125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/a59e9/4.webp 192w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/0ca9f/4.webp 384w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/dc9b9/4.webp 768w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/e2c2f/4.webp 1152w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/f3efb/4.webp 1536w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/18d98/4.webp 2312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/3b721/4.png 192w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/66595/4.png 384w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/fe486/4.png 768w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/d2d74/4.png 1152w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/e8464/4.png 1536w,\n/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/5dea3/4.png 2312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/9b2ecc9e09251b24a8294bdcfed829d3/fe486/4.png\" alt=\"4\" title=\"4\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>B.js 컴포넌트\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/5dea3/5.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 34.895833333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/a59e9/5.webp 192w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/0ca9f/5.webp 384w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/dc9b9/5.webp 768w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/e2c2f/5.webp 1152w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/f3efb/5.webp 1536w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/18d98/5.webp 2312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/3b721/5.png 192w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/66595/5.png 384w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/fe486/5.png 768w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/d2d74/5.png 1152w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/e8464/5.png 1536w,\n/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/5dea3/5.png 2312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/ea1e953f7bbead1707751c3733c6a42f/fe486/5.png\" alt=\"5\" title=\"5\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>A와 B는 이제 필요한 함수를 props로 전달받아서 이용할 수 있게 됐다.</p>\n<p>조금 더 나아가서 컴포넌트 이름을 App 단에서 정의하고 싶을 경우도 생각해 볼 수 있다.</p>\n<p>App.js\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/5dea3/6.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 22.395833333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAZElEQVQY06VP2wqAMBTan5xj284GtaIa/f+fGQsKeuvyoCKIqFtLYh56hpipAEWEqkoAlz7BmXXoApd54ziutGyMKRLoPpU1dY1yMtapcqqFZR4IH14V3hZ6H2jRDtPuiuivyzu7QW/zV6+jZAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/a59e9/6.webp 192w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/0ca9f/6.webp 384w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/dc9b9/6.webp 768w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/e2c2f/6.webp 1152w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/f3efb/6.webp 1536w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/18d98/6.webp 2312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/3b721/6.png 192w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/66595/6.png 384w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/fe486/6.png 768w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/d2d74/6.png 1152w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/e8464/6.png 1536w,\n/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/5dea3/6.png 2312w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/8617b9abe5ee2393566da849b3605ffe/fe486/6.png\" alt=\"6\" title=\"6\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이런 식으로 정의하게 되면 다음과 같은 흐름으로 name이 각 컴포넌트에 전달된다.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/221b9/7.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 16.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/a59e9/7.webp 192w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/0ca9f/7.webp 384w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/dc9b9/7.webp 768w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/e2c2f/7.webp 1152w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/f3efb/7.webp 1536w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/9e3d8/7.webp 3096w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/3b721/7.png 192w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/66595/7.png 384w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/fe486/7.png 768w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/d2d74/7.png 1152w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/e8464/7.png 1536w,\n/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/221b9/7.png 3096w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/795815a3935108510188e5ee094eb802/fe486/7.png\" alt=\"7\" title=\"7\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>화면에서 출력해 보면</p>\n<h1><img src=\"/71ac5c0906560f76eb927f2372d66df1/8.gif\"></h1>\n<p>A와 B 모두 잘 출력되는 것을 확인할 수 있다. 이렇게 HOC를 이용해 하나의 컴포넌트를 재사용해 A와 B의 중복된 로직을 제거할 수 있었다.</p>\n<p>HOC를 검색하다 관련 주제로 <strong>커링 (curring)</strong> 이라는 개념을 접하게 되었는데 커링은 어떤 것일까?</p>\n<h1>커링</h1>\n<hr>\n<p>커링의 정의는 <strong>다중 인수을 갖는 함수를 단일 인수를 갖는 함수들의 함수열로 바꾸는 것</strong> 으로 나와있다. 즉 내부에 인자를 받는 함수로 만들어 리턴하면 된다.</p>\n<p>예를 들면 다음과 같이 특정 학교의 반에 있는 학생의 점수를 얻는 함수가 있다고 해보자.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/13bda/9.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 17.1875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAgUlEQVQI132OSw7CMBDFepTmM8kkkzRNgXL/kxmpsEKChWW9jfWWWxVsVKIYkpVSK1kVLUo1QyTjvb9wzuE+Xtf1vb9YfIjMeWebT2rrjGNyPE5sM47zpI9BUqFtg7Hv1Nau+M9gDJGqhjVDtJFKx3omSCBIvAK5JKw1ihlR0t+HLxrLVt3gmhh8AAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/a59e9/9.webp 192w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/0ca9f/9.webp 384w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/dc9b9/9.webp 768w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/e2c2f/9.webp 1152w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/f3efb/9.webp 1536w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/bc5d9/9.webp 2220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/3b721/9.png 192w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/66595/9.png 384w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/fe486/9.png 768w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/d2d74/9.png 1152w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/e8464/9.png 1536w,\n/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/13bda/9.png 2220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/2751f93b0d52e9ea9e40678b040f5f99/fe486/9.png\" alt=\"9\" title=\"9\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>위 함수를 출력하면 결과는 잘 나오지만 아쉬운 점이 한 가지 있는데, 정상적인 출력값을 얻으려면 모든 인자를 항상 보내줘야 한다는 점이다.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/13bda/10.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 25.520833333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/a59e9/10.webp 192w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/0ca9f/10.webp 384w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/dc9b9/10.webp 768w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/e2c2f/10.webp 1152w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/f3efb/10.webp 1536w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/bc5d9/10.webp 2220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/3b721/10.png 192w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/66595/10.png 384w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/fe486/10.png 768w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/d2d74/10.png 1152w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/e8464/10.png 1536w,\n/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/13bda/10.png 2220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/341e84e1e11dff38ea93964382407722/fe486/10.png\" alt=\"10\" title=\"10\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>같은 학교와 반의 학생에 대한 정보를 얻는데도 매번 같은 인자를 보내야 한다. 왜냐하면 함수는 한번 호출되면 자신이 실행되었던 환경을 모두 잊어버리기 때문이다. 커링을 사용해서 위 함수를 개선해 보자.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/13bda/11.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 34.375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/a59e9/11.webp 192w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/0ca9f/11.webp 384w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/dc9b9/11.webp 768w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/e2c2f/11.webp 1152w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/f3efb/11.webp 1536w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/bc5d9/11.webp 2220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/3b721/11.png 192w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/66595/11.png 384w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/fe486/11.png 768w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/d2d74/11.png 1152w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/e8464/11.png 1536w,\n/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/13bda/11.png 2220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/235edb8838bd474451ebf9d2a1e78676/fe486/11.png\" alt=\"11\" title=\"11\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>이제는 이전처럼 학교와 반에 대한 정보를 매번 보내 줄 필요 없이 학생의 정보만 보내주면 된다. 학교 이름과 반에 대한 정보는 처음 getGrade 함수를 실행할 때 고정한 채로 리턴했기 때문이다. 즉 클로저를 이용해 school과 _class를 자유 변수로 만들고 내부 함수에서 기억하는 형태라고 생각할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>ES6 화살표 함수를 이용해 getGrade 함수의 형태를 좀 더 짧게 변형 시킬 수 있다.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/13bda/12.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 27.604166666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/a59e9/12.webp 192w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/0ca9f/12.webp 384w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/dc9b9/12.webp 768w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/e2c2f/12.webp 1152w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/f3efb/12.webp 1536w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/bc5d9/12.webp 2220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/3b721/12.png 192w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/66595/12.png 384w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/fe486/12.png 768w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/d2d74/12.png 1152w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/e8464/12.png 1536w,\n/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/13bda/12.png 2220w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/b256628a9205e4296154a5c6b3328e43/fe486/12.png\" alt=\"12\" title=\"12\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>일반적으로 커링은 composition 패턴과 같이 이용된다고 하기 때문에 다른 예제로 사용법을 알아보자. composition을 이용하면 쉽게 함수를 조합할 수 있다.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/8ac3b/13.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 44.27083333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/a59e9/13.webp 192w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/0ca9f/13.webp 384w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/dc9b9/13.webp 768w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/e2c2f/13.webp 1152w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/f3efb/13.webp 1536w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/1c319/13.webp 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/3b721/13.png 192w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/66595/13.png 384w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/fe486/13.png 768w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/d2d74/13.png 1152w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/e8464/13.png 1536w,\n/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/8ac3b/13.png 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/4a980f9994d4f779fc6d301c159ab6bb/fe486/13.png\" alt=\"13\" title=\"13\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>위 코드에서 changeUserData 함수는 user 객체를 받아 fullName과 주소를 추가하고 first, last Name은 지우는 역할을 하고 있다.\n만약 해당 함수를 이용할 때 특정 조건일 경우엔 주소를 추가하고 싶지 않다면 어떻게 할 수 있을까?</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/8ac3b/14.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 35.416666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/a59e9/14.webp 192w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/0ca9f/14.webp 384w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/dc9b9/14.webp 768w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/e2c2f/14.webp 1152w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/f3efb/14.webp 1536w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/1c319/14.webp 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/3b721/14.png 192w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/66595/14.png 384w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/fe486/14.png 768w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/d2d74/14.png 1152w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/e8464/14.png 1536w,\n/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/8ac3b/14.png 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/9bfef9912c097d7ed2562a30de0b5729/fe486/14.png\" alt=\"14\" title=\"14\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>이렇게 if 문을 사용해서 함수 내부에 조건을 거는 방법이 있다. <strong>그렇다면 이것의 문제점은 무엇일까?</strong>\n만약 요구사항이 추가돼서 user.id가 1,3,5일 경우 주소를 추가하지 않으려 하고 user.id 9는 fullName을 추가하고 싶지 않아 한다.</p>\n<p>요구사항을 해결하기 위해 <strong>기존에 작성했던 함수의 내부 로직을 아래와 같이 다시 건드려야 한다.</strong></p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/8ac3b/15.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 33.854166666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/a59e9/15.webp 192w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/0ca9f/15.webp 384w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/dc9b9/15.webp 768w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/e2c2f/15.webp 1152w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/f3efb/15.webp 1536w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/1c319/15.webp 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/3b721/15.png 192w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/66595/15.png 384w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/fe486/15.png 768w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/d2d74/15.png 1152w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/e8464/15.png 1536w,\n/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/8ac3b/15.png 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/4d4d7c888c78515b58d05bf197a853dc/fe486/15.png\" alt=\"15\" title=\"15\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>만약 또 요구사항이 바뀌면 다시 작성했던 함수를 고쳐야하고, 이렇게 고쳐야하는 함수가 1개가 아니라 몇 십 몇 백개라고 하면\n일일히 찾아다니면서 수정해야하는 수고스러움이 들게 된다. 그중엔 반드시 실수도 일어날 수 있다.</p>\n<p>따라서 함수의 기능을 분리하고 조합을 이용해 다시 작성해 보자.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/8ac3b/16.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 33.854166666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/a59e9/16.webp 192w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/0ca9f/16.webp 384w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/dc9b9/16.webp 768w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/e2c2f/16.webp 1152w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/f3efb/16.webp 1536w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/1c319/16.webp 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/3b721/16.png 192w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/66595/16.png 384w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/fe486/16.png 768w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/d2d74/16.png 1152w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/e8464/16.png 1536w,\n/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/8ac3b/16.png 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/dd7bbce7ecd17946ae0f371d720d2e21/fe486/16.png\" alt=\"16\" title=\"16\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>먼저 함수를 위와 같이 기능별로 분리해 줄 수 있다. 함수당 하나의 역할만 할 수 있도록 최소화해준다.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/8ac3b/17.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 10.416666666666668%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAATUlEQVQI143MMQ6AMAxD0R4lCSmJW6ou3P9qRkXqDIPl5euV+zqJOVijMxJMNGY2Hu40M4oIVfVzuyuixsBgoDMxXjBiwaB7/QXuZv0D09Y4hLLtkf4AAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/a59e9/17.webp 192w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/0ca9f/17.webp 384w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/dc9b9/17.webp 768w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/e2c2f/17.webp 1152w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/f3efb/17.webp 1536w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/1c319/17.webp 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/3b721/17.png 192w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/66595/17.png 384w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/fe486/17.png 768w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/d2d74/17.png 1152w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/e8464/17.png 1536w,\n/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/8ac3b/17.png 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/8f24df3fef0f108be85bfaab7306936f/fe486/17.png\" alt=\"17\" title=\"17\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>함수를 조합할 수 있는 compose 함수를 생성해 주었다. compose 함수의 원리는 다음과 같다.</p>\n<p>user 객체 => fns 중 첫 번째 함수의 인자로 user를 넣고 실행 => 반환값을 acc에 할당 => acc를 두 번째 함수에 넣고 실행 => 반환 => … fns가 없을 때까지 반복.</p>\n<p>이렇게 compose를 이용하면 기존 데이터에 기능을 추가해서 원하는 형태로 가공할 수 있다. 이제 compose를 이용해 보자.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/8ac3b/18.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 19.270833333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAjUlEQVQY04WOSwrDMBBDc5PMhNqej+M4TQmlkNL7X0olH7qsF0IPLR7qvBpuyRGSIIlCRBFCxDAMYCIQEZj5Yj75T7ooGTpWiBWoZ4g6VA0ickqZQdRfTW1hyQu8vjAub2hZYWXFeN+Q5w02PTE9PkiaQX3flB1CiYZkFeLz0UEc4vvjnfOxh6i/ly3hFyBwcrjW4F9oAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/a59e9/18.webp 192w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/0ca9f/18.webp 384w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/dc9b9/18.webp 768w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/e2c2f/18.webp 1152w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/f3efb/18.webp 1536w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/1c319/18.webp 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/3b721/18.png 192w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/66595/18.png 384w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/fe486/18.png 768w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/d2d74/18.png 1152w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/e8464/18.png 1536w,\n/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/8ac3b/18.png 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/d0673895c7cd2c145030c94c0d10cbb8/fe486/18.png\" alt=\"18\" title=\"18\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>compose로 함수를 조합해 새로운 함수를 만들었다.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/8ac3b/19.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 30.208333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/a59e9/19.webp 192w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/0ca9f/19.webp 384w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/dc9b9/19.webp 768w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/e2c2f/19.webp 1152w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/f3efb/19.webp 1536w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/1c319/19.webp 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/3b721/19.png 192w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/66595/19.png 384w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/fe486/19.png 768w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/d2d74/19.png 1152w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/e8464/19.png 1536w,\n/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/8ac3b/19.png 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/83b1fd4de896af08d987357cb6185ab0/fe486/19.png\" alt=\"19\" title=\"19\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>이렇게 원하는 함수를 골라 사용할 수 있기 때문에 <strong>이제 기존 함수를 수정하지 않고도 원하는 요구사항을 들어줄 수 있다.</strong></p>\n<p>compose 함수를 reduce 없이 어떻게 만들 수 있을까? 여러 가지 방법이 있겠지만 이렇게 만들 수 있을 것 같다.</p>\n<h1><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/8ac3b/20.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/a59e9/20.webp 192w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/0ca9f/20.webp 384w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/dc9b9/20.webp 768w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/e2c2f/20.webp 1152w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/f3efb/20.webp 1536w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/1c319/20.webp 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/3b721/20.png 192w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/66595/20.png 384w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/fe486/20.png 768w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/d2d74/20.png 1152w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/e8464/20.png 1536w,\n/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/8ac3b/20.png 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/a1f7a8e2bf25e2dce35f1d8916e7afb5/fe486/20.png\" alt=\"20\" title=\"20\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></h1>\n<p>똑같이 잘 작동하는 것을 확인할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>ES5로도 만들어 보았다.\n<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/8ac3b/21.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 30.208333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAGCAYAAADDl76dAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAg0lEQVQY06WPyw6CQBAE90+cWWYfsIDyyPL/X1YGo4l6Ejx0+tKpVLu1j+ShEGJHmwsWEqKKiqB7/xh57p2o5zpWpnljWSspt4hcTsH2dqpCN0wst5lg9rB7Hxw3FCHmzFo3aq2U0h8Cfcd572lCJPUjqe2w3fIfYGOGt/Bx88zlF/AOAgWoW/fiJ/sAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source srcset=\"/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/a59e9/21.webp 192w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/0ca9f/21.webp 384w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/dc9b9/21.webp 768w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/e2c2f/21.webp 1152w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/f3efb/21.webp 1536w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/1c319/21.webp 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n          <source srcset=\"/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/3b721/21.png 192w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/66595/21.png 384w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/fe486/21.png 768w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/d2d74/21.png 1152w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/e8464/21.png 1536w,\n/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/8ac3b/21.png 2684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" type=\"image/png\">\n          <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/390388e68c77d368a08edb34a77acf32/fe486/21.png\" alt=\"21\" title=\"21\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<h1>정리</h1>\n<hr>\n<p>지금까지 HOC와 커링 &#x26; 컴포지션에 대해 간략하게 알아보았다. HOC를 사용하면 컴포넌트를 쉽게 재사용할 수 있지만 HOC의 복잡성과 디버깅 문제로 인해 최근에는 <strong>custom hook을 이용해 쉽게 컴포넌트를 재사용</strong> 할 수 있다고 한다.</p>\n<p>이번 포스트는 HOC와 커링에 관한 주제이기 때문에 다루지 않고 관련 링크를 남기겠다.</p>\n<p>개인적으로 함수를 조합해서 사용할 수 있다는 점이 굉장히 흥미롭게 느껴졌다. 간단한 토이 프로젝트로 적용해 보고 싶다.</p>\n<h1>참고</h1>\n<hr>\n<h3>블로그</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ko.reactjs.org/docs/higher-order-components.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">리액트 공식문서 react-HOC</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://devcore.io/en/react/hocs-vs-hooks-what-to-use-and-why/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">HOCs vs HOOKs</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://flexiple.com/react/introduction-to-higher-order-components-in-react-by-example/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">HOC란?</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ko.javascript.info/currying-partials\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">모던 자바스크립트 - 커링</a></p>\n<h3>유튜브</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jlLTcYdjo9I&#x26;list=PLEOnZ6GeucBVixAJGEnHvcGjzz1yrTyfO&#x26;index=4&#x26;t=1682s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">커링과 컴포지션</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"컴포넌트 재사용하기와 HOC, + 커링","summary":"어떻게 해야 컴포넌트를 재사용할 수 있을까?","date":"2022.05.10.","categories":["TIL","React"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/b3221240861b7e5156657631edc409d2/afa5c/TIL.png","srcSet":"/static/b3221240861b7e5156657631edc409d2/2fe1e/TIL.png 480w,\n/static/b3221240861b7e5156657631edc409d2/9bec7/TIL.png 960w,\n/static/b3221240861b7e51566576